              <span id="reviewTextContainer3282805522" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9499603231540479959">This book made me think A LOT, which is why I would recommend that everyone read it, regardless of your beliefs. The book has a not-so-thin veil of arrogance that I had to overlook, and I didn’t agree with everything, but there were things that really resonated with me. Reading this book forced me to think critically and that was cool. </span>

          </span>
