<span id="freeTextContainer4563237544185641289">Yikes....well I&apos;m not religious at all, but this was not that interesting or enlightening to me. I definitely prefer Richard Dawkins when it comes to atheism, critical thought, and religion. I also thought Boghossian was too angry and I rather have a rational/non-emotional approach to anything philosophical.</span>
  <span id="freeText4563237544185641289" style="display:none">Yikes....well I'm not religious at all, but this was not that interesting or enlightening to me. I definitely prefer Richard Dawkins when it comes to atheism, critical thought, and religion. I also thought Boghossian was too angry and I rather have a rational/non-emotional approach to anything philosophical.</span>
