<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22571733-galileo-s-middle-finger"><img alt="Galileo&#39;s Middle Finger: Heretics, Activists, and the Search for Justice in Science" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1406513188l/22571733._SX98_.jpg" />
